snippet.title: SEC Chairman Gensler Says Bitcoin Competes w/ U.S. Banking System
snippet.description:
Recap of everything Bitcoin for Dec, 1st 2021
► SEC chairman Gary Gensler says Bitcoin competes with the U.S. banking system. He states Bitcoin was created as a “reaction” to the U.S. monetary system. Gensler believes that their digital money system was created with money laundering sanction and reims around the globe. Join us today talking about this bullsh*t. 

► Crypto scammers during the month of October stole around $9 million by defrauding victims though fake Youtube giveaway scams.
